OL,3,CNew documentary by Kate Garraway to
OL,4,Cshow final year of husband's life
OL,6,FThe final year of former political
OL,7,Fadvisor Derek Draper's life will be
OL,8,Ftold by his widow Kate Garraway in a
OL,9,Fnew ITV documentary.
OL,11,FIn Kate Garraway: Derek's Story, the
OL,12,FGood Morning Britain presenter will
OL,13,Fexplore her husband's struggles as he
OL,14,Fsuffered long-lasting symptoms from
OL,15,Fcoronavirus and required daily care.
OL,17,FThe film will also highlight the cost
OL,18,Fof caring for a loved one in the UK.
