OL,3,CNew documentary by Kate Garraway to
OL,4,Cshow final year of husband's life
OL,6,Fpreviously chronicled the impact of
OL,7,Fcaring for her husband, who died aged
OL,8,F56 in January after suffering a
OL,9,Fcardiac arrest, in two other ITV
OL,10,Fdocumentaries.
OL,12,FBefore his death, the former lobbyist
OL,13,Fsaid he wanted the public to "hear"
OL,14,Fhis story, and when asked why, he
OL,15,Fadded: "I want to be heard."
OL,17,FGarraway said: "Obviously, when we
OL,18,Fstarted making this documentary early
OL,19,Flast year, we had no idea the events
OL,20,Fthat would unfold that ultimately took
OL,21,FDerek from us.
