OL,6,F"And in January 2024, I wondered if it
OL,7,Fwas right that it should ever come to
OL,8,Fair.
OL,10,F"But I didn't want to let those who
OL,11,Fhave given us so much support over the
OL,12,Flast four years down, and the carers
OL,13,Fpaid and unpaid who, in their
OL,14,Fthousands of letters to me, feel
OL,15,FDerek's story has given them a voice.
OL,17,F"Also, I remembered so vividly that
OL,18,Fthe idea of making this third
OL,19,Fdocumentary at all came from Derek
OL,20,Fhimself."
