OL,6,FTune into the ITV News entertainment
OL,7,Fpodcast, Unscripted...
OL,9,FThe first instalment, Finding Derek `
OL,10,Fwhich was about her family's
OL,11,Fexperience during the pandemic and
OL,12,Fdetailed her husband's treatment and
OL,13,Fhis return to their family home ` won
OL,14,FGarraway the documentary prize at the
OL,15,F2021 National Television Awards (NTA).
OL,17,FIt was followed with Caring For Derek,
OL,18,Fwhich showed the "myriad challenges of
OL,19,Fthe social care system and its
OL,20,Fcomplexities", and earned her the same
OL,21,FNTA gong.
