OL,3,CNew documentary by Kate Garraway to
OL,4,Cshow final year of husband's life
OL,6,FThe new documentary charts Draper's
OL,7,Frelationship with his wife ` who he
OL,8,Fmarried in 2005 and the pair had two
OL,9,Fchildren, Darcey and Billy ` and how
OL,10,Fthe illness changed their lives, along
OL,11,Fwith his experiences before Covid,
OL,12,Fincluding his political career.
OL,14,FGarraway said: "I am delighted that
OL,15,Fthe film is a tribute to Derek, his
OL,16,Fincredible spirit and a tribute to all
OL,17,Fof those who fight on to make every
OL,18,Fsecond of life count, whatever is
OL,19,Fthrown at them."
