OL,3,CNew documentary by Kate Garraway to
OL,4,Cshow final year of husband's life
OL,6,FIn the 1990s, Draper was a prominent
OL,7,Ffigure in New Labour, working for
OL,8,FPeter Mandelson and setting up the
OL,9,Fcentre-left pressure group Progress
OL,10,Fwith Liam Byrne, who went on to become
OL,11,Fa Labour MP.
OL,13,FHe later founded and edited the
OL,14,FLabourList news site before stepping
OL,15,Fdown in 2009.
OL,17,FThere are also contributions in the
OL,18,Fdocumentary from Jake, the care worker
OL,19,Fwho supported Draper, and Kathryn
OL,20,FSmith, chief executive of charity the
OL,21,FSocial Care Institute for Excellence.
