OL,3,CNew documentary by Kate Garraway to
OL,4,Cshow final year of husband's life
OL,6,FJo Clinton-Davis, controller of
OL,7,Ffactual at ITV, said: "We can see in
OL,8,FDerek Draper's story the individual
OL,9,Ftragedy of a life devastated by
OL,10,Fillness, but also the wider
OL,11,Fperspective of how a family is
OL,12,Fimpacted.
OL,14,F"Derek's desire for his story to be
OL,15,Ffilmed, along with Kate in their home,
OL,16,Fprovides an insight into both their
OL,17,Fpersonal struggles as well
OL,18,Fhighlighting the exhausting challenges
OL,19,Fof caring for a family member in the
OL,20,Fhome within our care system."
