OL,6,FIn February, a funeral for Draper was
OL,7,Fattended by former prime minister Sir
OL,8,FTony Blair, musician Sir Elton John,
OL,9,Fex-cabinet minister Lord Mandelson and
OL,10,FLabour leader Sir Keir Starmer.
OL,12,FGarraway took a brief absence from
OL,13,FSmooth Radio and GMB after Draper's
OL,14,Fdeath before returning and thanking
OL,15,Fher audiences for their support.
