OL,6,FColleen Flynn, executive producer at
OL,7,FFlicker Productions, said: "We thank
OL,8,FKate and Derek for sharing their story
OL,9,Fat the most intimate of times and hope
OL,10,Fthat this film goes some way to
OL,11,Fhighlighting the need for the positive
OL,12,Fchange they both hoped for within the
OL,13,Fcare system."
